"1/4 cup olive oil","1  small shallot, minced","1  clove garlic, minced","10 ounce fresh mushrooms, trimmed, coarsely chopped","  Salt and pepper","2 tablespoons chopped fresh parsley","2 teaspoons lemon juice","16  slices French or Italian bread, cut diagonally about 1/2 inch thick","6 ounces soft goat cheese, at room temperature"